{{Top|leg}}
'''Bubble-and-squirt''' was a term used by [[Whie Malreaux/Legends|Whie Malreaux]] to describe the strange food served onboard the ''[[Reasonable Doubt]]''. It came in multiple sizes, including 'large'.

{{Food-stub}}

==Behind the scenes==
Bubble-and-squirt may be a reference to the traditional English dish of [[Wikipedia:Bubble and squeak|Bubble and squeak]].

